nges; isFirstRender and onRefreshTree are unstable","Update the dependencies array to be: [constructObjectTree, currentSelectedDatabase, dataSource, dataSourceMDSId, isObjectLoading, setToast, updateDatabaseState]",{"range":"1496","text":"1497"},"only re-run when isObjectLoading changes; other deps (setToast, constructObjectTree, etc.) are unstable","Update the dependencies array to be: [stopDatabasesLoading, stopLoadingAccelerations, stopLoadingTables]",{"range":"1498","text":"1499"},"cleanup should only run on unmount","Update the dependencies array to be: [currentQueryHandler, selectedItems, http, setToast]",{"range":"1500","text":"1501"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [selectedItems, refreshTree, getSidebarContent]",{"range":"1502","text":"1503"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [accelerationFormData, accelerationFormData.dataTable, setAccelerationFormData]",{"range":"1504","text":"1505"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [http, setToast]",{"range":"1506","text":"1507"},"setToast is unstable (new ref every render) and would cause infinite loops","Update the dependencies array to be: [loadDataSource]",{"range":"1508","text":"1509"},"loadDataSource is unstable; should only run on mount","Update the dependencies array to be: [accelerationFormData.dataSource, loadDatabases]",{"range":"1510","text":"1511"},"loadDatabases is unstable; only re-run when dataSource changes","Update the dependencies array to be: [accelerationFormData.database, loadTables]",{"range":"1512","text":"1513"},"loadTables is unstable; only re-run when database changes","Update the dependencies array to be: [accelerationFormData.dataTableFields, setAccelerationFormData]",{"range":"1514","text":"1515"},"setAccelerationFormData excluded to prevent re-render loop when form data reference changes","Update the dependencies array to be: [accelerationFormData, accelerationFormData.dataTableFields, setAccelerationFormData]",{"range":"1516","text":"1517"},[3106,3151],"[selectedItems, refre